{"tid":2002755,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局致函全港校長 提醒學生不應戴口罩","createTime":"2020-05-05T11:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T11:39:58.000Z","uid":112747,"like":19,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f7c38e34c6b69fe9678ec5b7dc5ad8cbba31b0","tid":2002755,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"復課戴唔戴得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局致函全港校長，提醒學生校內或校外均不應戴口罩。 <br />\n教育局今午致函全港學校、校監及校長，提醒《禁止蒙面規例》明日正式生效，為免誤墮法網，原則上學生在校內或校外均不應戴口罩，或以任何其他方式遮蓋臉孔，有宗教或健康原因除外。而這原則亦通用於所有教職員及在學校工作的人，例如課外活動導師，由服務供應商派往學校提供服務的人員等。<br />\n局方促請學校在這原則上訂定校本的處理方法，包括如何處理沒有依從指示的學生及其他人士。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365086&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365086%26refer%3DShare&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktQZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=fcff9529\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365086%26refer%3DShare&h=455c88e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365086&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"bde99faacad48d4bd38df45d56d285aa20d2a4b5","tid":2002755,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"朋友做教師，聽講都要呈報Websams,唔俾帶"},{"pid":"880628242c00b264a7bac216029199a02d8f21e1","tid":2002755,"uid":25601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"姐係點呀 一返學戴口罩就犯法呀 唔戴就會增加感染機會"},{"pid":"be9cb356f3c879e96b3c1bfb8c814e4abd534347","tid":2002755,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"Sir 我啱啱食完袋底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497c02cd7a8d59f9f11e1dcfd32e5fd6ae6e68b8","tid":2002755,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"co